<ArticleLayout
  title="Truck-Mount vs Portable Machines"
  description="Side-by-side comparison between grocery-store rental machines and professional truck-mount carpet cleaning units in terms of power, heat and drying time."
>
  <p>In carpet cleaning, equipment quality changes results dramatically. The difference between a small portable unit and a professional truck-mount is significant.</p>

  <h2>Heat</h2>
  <p>Truck-mount systems maintain high and stable water temperature, which helps dissolve grease and embedded soil more effectively than low-power portable systems.</p>

  <h2>Extraction power</h2>
  <p>Higher vacuum power means better water recovery and faster drying. Strong extraction reduces overwetting risk and helps carpets dry in hours, not days.</p>

  <h2>Operational efficiency</h2>
  <p>A truck-mount setup is built for consistent pressure, heat, and airflow during the full job, which improves reliability on large or heavily soiled areas.</p>
</ArticleLayout>
